Package: simts
Title: Simulate Time Series
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Leon", "Fernandes", , "leon.fernandes@columbia.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7192-9939"))
Description: Simulates data from various time series models. Also includes
        helper functions to specify as well as extract underlying model
        parameters from fitted objects.
